erpret observed galaxy\nspectral energy distributions may not be appropriate to constrain the physical\nparameters of star-forming galaxies at intermediate redshifts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Oct 2012 20:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Dec 2012 21:00:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
