 since for quarks J^{\\delta,\\delta}_q ~ 1 and\nJ^{-\\delta,\\delta}_q ~ \\sqrt{\\tau}, then the dipole dependence is realized when\n\\tau >> 1 in the case when the quark transitions with spin-flip are dominate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Oct 2012 02:15:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Feb 2013 21:24:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-05"}
